Package: brainconn
Title: Plotting Tool for Brain Connectivity Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Sidhant", "Chopra", email = "sid.chopra@monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This package mainly contatins two plotting fucntions: `brianconn()` and `brainconn3d()`, as well as data for several commonly used MNI-space brain atlases
